         <abstract>
            <p>This paper is concerned with the numerical approximation of the best possible constants $\gamma_{n,k}$ in the inequality $$\|F^{(k)}\|^2 \leqslant \gamma^{-1}_{n,k} \{\|F\|^2 + \|F^{(n)}\|^2\},$$ where $$\|F\|^2 = \int^\infty_0 |F(x)|^2 dx.$$ A list of all constants $\gamma_{n,k}$ for $n \leqslant 10$ is given.</p>
